Directed by Namrata Singh Gujral

Written by Denise Cruz-Castino. Andy Glickman. Namrata Singh Gujral

Cast Nargis Fakhri (Shania Dhaliwal). Abhimanue Kamboj (Salman). Rajkummar Rao (Officer Harbhajan Singh). Bo Derek (Mandy Singh). Candy Clark (Claudia Burrell). Saru Maini (Bhavna). Anneliese van der Pol (Whitney Simmons). Suvinder Vicky (SSP Avtar Singh Gill). Mariana Paola Vicente (Alexa DuPont). Robert Palmer Watkins (Mark Cottell). Dawn Richard (Lydia Duniyar) . Ravi Aneja (Donald). Darshan Aulakh (Parveen Singh). Ramesh Bhardwaj (Harpreet’s Dad). Bagga Cheema (Gopi). Diljott (Harleen). Rupak Ginn (Rajinder Singh Dhaliwal). Pooja Gujral (Sarla Bhain Ji). Jahir Islam (Shahed akbar). Isabella Jem (Young Shania Dhaliwal). Abhimanue Kamboj (Salman (as Abhimanue)). BÃ©rangÃ¨re Rochet (Alexa, Devika et Harleen (voice)). Shiwani Saini (Devika). Ramniq Sandhu (Rani). Neil Singh (Chahel Singh). Kamlesh Walia (Old lady)

Producers Shivam Aggarwal. Zeeshan Ahmad. Darshan Aulakh. Jasmine Singh Cooper. Joe Cooper. Nayomi Cooper. Amy Ghosh. Namrata Singh Gujral. Robin Mackenzie. S.R. Miller. Mark Napier. Sumeet Sachdev. Shivv Sharma. R.Z. Shedlock. Jasjeet Singh
